#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Regardless of their name, these properties still make sense for Hibernate Reactive."
msgstr "Independentemente do nome, essas propriedades ainda fazem sentido para o Hibernate Reactive."

